programme.title: Khazanah Borneo Ep3
programme.desc: Kisah pengembaraan peninggalan sejarah di Sabah dan Sarawak yang melibatkan banyak kesan-kesan sejarah dari alam semulajadi dan juga dari peninggalan jajahan kolonialis serta prasejarah. Turut dikongsikan latar belakang kajian arkeologi, nilai-nilai sejarah. aktiviti konservasi dan usaha-usaha untuk menjadikan lokasi-lokasi ini sebagai tarikan pelancongan. Dalam episod ini ke Lembah Mansuli di Lahad Datu yang merupakan lembah yang tertua daripada segi prasejarahnya di Borneo, meningkatkan kefahaman budaya masyarakat Paleolitik di Sabah dan Asia Tenggara dari segi perubahan teknologi alat batu dan hubungan dengan persekitaran terutamanya turun naik paras laut dalam #KhazanahBorneo

programme.desc: Program majalah animasi kanak-kanak yang mengisahkan tentang Uwais bersama kawan-kawannya, Sidek dan Ahmad yang membantu sesiapa sahaja yang memerlukan bantuan. Episod kali ini mengisahkan Uwais dan Sidek pergi ke Kampung Andalas untuk memberikan bekalan ubat kepada penduduk di situ. Penduduk Kampung Andalas diserang beruang pada waktu malam. Uwais dan Sidek membantu mereka. Rupa-rupanya beruang tersebut adalah manusia yang ingin mencuri makanan dan barang keperluan yang lain dalam #GengUwais

programme.title: Widuri : Zuriat Dari Penjara Ep23
programme.desc: Zaman dan Erina di amanahkan menjaga zuriat dari penjara. Zuriat itu adalah dari isteri pertamanya Shara yang di penjarakan kerana kesalahan mengedar dadah. Dalam episod ini Shara telah meninggal dunia kerana pendarahan di dalam otak akibat tekanan darah yang sangat tinggi. Hubungan Zaman dan Erina kurang baik sejak ibu bapa Erina meninggal dunia. Pak Ngah Erina selalu memburukkan Zaman. Zaman selalu keluar kerana tidak mahu bergaduh dengan Erina. Sebelum meninggal dunia, Shara telah mahu anaknya Rizky di jaga oleh Zaman. Lakonan Wafariena Roslan, Josiah Hogan, Rasya Dean, Linda Rafar, Syed Aiman, Addam Roslan, Nurul Harisyah,Mubarak Majid, Aliza Rafar, JC Lim dalam WIDURI #ZuriatDariPenjara

Lalu Hafiz perkenalkan Ariana sebagai kekasihnya kepada Irsya. Pada masa yang sama, Hafiz juga minta nombor telefon Irsya kerana dia nak hubungi Irsya untuk iklan syarikatnya.

programme.title: Jom Masak Ep1
programme.desc: Minggu ini jom masak bersama Syukor Adan & Isteri untuk menampilkan resepi dari mereka. Jom Masak adalah sebuah rancangan masakan melibatkan Pemain Bola Sepak bagi setiap episod . Ia turut diselitkan dengan unsur sketsa dan komedi untuk menjadikan rancangan ini lebih menarik dan menghiburkan penonton . Rancangan ini turut memberikan tip masakan kepada penonton mengikut petua-petua dalam menyediakan masakan yang enak.

programme.title: #ustazmasak S2 Ep02
programme.desc: Dalam rancangan ini dalam setiap episod Cef Fendi dan Ustaz Jemputan yang berlainan di setiap episode akan mengembara ke destinasi seperti ladang dan tempat perusahaan makanan yang berasaskan bahan masakan yang sering digunakan untuk memasak. programme.title: Aku Kata A, A!
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Amin yang bekerja di sebuah kilang terpikat dengan Aida yang berasal dari Kelantan selepas mereka terlanggar di tempat kerja. Apabila Amin semakin mesra dengan Aida, dia didampingi Iqbal yang mengugutnya supaya menjauhi Aida. Mira yang merupakan jiran kepada Amin sebenarnya jatuh hati dengannya. Hari-hari Mira cuba mengambil hati mak dan ayah Amin dengan memberi kuih. Siapakah yang akan menjadi pilihan Amin?

Tiga orang tetamu menyertai pertandingan ikat sampin dan memakai talileher.

programme.title: Cahaya Di Hujung Nyawa S1 Ep16
programme.desc: Hud (Razali Hussien) merupakan seorang wartawan telah membuat laporan penyiasatan ekslusif tentang kejadian tanah runtuh di sebuah taman tema. Ia berpunca daripada pembangunan yang tidak menepati piawaian alam sekitar sehingga taman tema itu diarahkan tutup. Tiara (Faradhiya) pula seorang aktivis alam sekitar begitu tertarik kepada Hud kerana keberaniannya menentang penjenayah alam sekitar. Namun, Tiara yang baru pulang dari luar negara, tidak menyedari yang penjenayah itu adalah bapanya sendiri, Tan Sri Selamat Rahmat.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep11
programme.desc: Memaparkan puan Sarah bertanyakan tentang Melissa, Melissa hanya menjawab ketika Syakir tiada, dia ada juga tinggal di sini sebaliknya berulang dari Cheras dan datang sendiri. Ketika puan Sarah tiada, Nora meluahkan perasaannya termasuk seolah-olah dia tidak sukakan kepada puan Sarah dan suaminya. Isunya sehingga ini dia tidak merasai perutnya telah berisi, asyik minum air akar kayu. Nora meluahkan kepada orang gaji. Dia tidak perasaan Shamsul terdengar. Lalu Shamsul terasa dia juga bersalah ketika menceritakan hal itu kepada Syakir. Syakir dapat menasihat Shamsul baik juga mereka berpindah dan tinggal berasingan. Sehingga kini Syakir masih tidak balik dan Melissa setakat ini berjaya "menyamar" sebagai pembantu rumah. Sementara puan Sarah berehat, Melissa telah siap makan malam. Apabila Syakir balik makan malam telah siap, sekali gus Melissa dapat berlagak sebagai pembantu rumah. Selepas makan malam puan Sarah balik. Melissa juga berpura-pura akan balik. Melissa akui dia akan balik sendiri dan akui tidak pernah sekalipun Syakir menghantar dia pulang. Puan Sarah yang balik ke rumah menceritakan kepada suaminya, Shamsul dan Nora. Ketika di tapak perumahan semasa Shamsul dan Syakir melawat, sempat Syakir menceritakan yang ibu mereka datang mengejut ke rumahnya. Shamsul tahu dan mereka juga berbual yang Syakir ada "mate" muda dan cantik pula. Syakir menyatakan dia sebenarnya pembantu di cafe tetapi untuk dia perolehi gaji lebih, dia dijadikankan pembantu di rumah. Sementara itu Melissa mula terasa rendah diri kerana kini dia tahu taraf suami dan keluarganya. Sebenarnya selepas puan Sarah balik, Syakir hanya menemani ibunya makan,. Syakir kali ini memanaskan luak dan hidangkan semula. Dia tahu Melissa belum makan. Melissa diajak makan bersama. Melissa cuba berdalih pun begitu Melissa terpaksa akur dan hasrat Syakir dia ingin makan bersama Melissa. Esoknya, dengan tiba-tiba puan Sarah mengunjungi lagi ke rumah Syakir. Ketika itu Melissa masih berkemas di luar kawasan rumah. Agak tergamam Melissa apabila puan Sarah meminta dia ganti pakaian dan ikutnya. Kelam kabut dibuat Melissa, akhirnya puan Sarah meminta dia teman ke pasaraya dan membawa barang belian. Semasa kelam kabut di pasaraya, Engku Razi juga melalui di pasaraya dan terlanggar Melissa dan Engku Razi sekadar terlihat mukanya. Lepas membeli belah terus Melissa di bawa ke rumah puan Sarah dan Melissa diminta siapkan masakan makan malam keluarganya. Syakir berkongsi pengalaman terakhir apa yang berlaku antara dirinya, ibu dan isterinya dengan Jenny. Jenny meminta dia bersedia sekarang. Syakir yang diminta bapanya makan malam bersekali. Makanan dihidangkan oleh Melissa dan alangkah terperanjatnya Syakir melihat Melissa. Sebelum itu Melissa tahu yang dia tidak setaraf dengan keluarga suaminya. Razi ketika di rumah terimbas Melissa dan meminatinya.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep43
programme.desc: Mengangkat kisah cinta segitiga antara Riri (Aurelia), Bandi (Ricky Harun), dan Haris (Ali Syakieb). Riri seorang mahasiswi kedokteran yang merasa jenuh dengan hidupnya yang penuh aturan, bertemu dengan Bandi yang menderita penyakit jantung kronis. Bandi jatuh hati pada pandangan pertama dengan Riri, merasakan semangat yang baru untuk kesembuhannya. Sementara kakaknya, Haris, justru cemas kehadiran Riri akan memberi harapan palsu untuk Bandi.

programme.title: Jodoh Sebelah Pintu S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Mona semakin muak dengan cubaan Irfan untuk merapatinya. Dia akhirnya mendapatkan bantuan Cikgu Farhan untuk mematikan niat Irfan. Badrul pula yang mula rasa cemburu. Dia cuba membantu Irfan mendapatkan Mona semula. Tanpa pengetahuan Badrul, ibu bapanya telah meneruskan pertunangan dengan Mona. Daripada Alang, Mona akhirnya mendapat tahu bahawa lelaki itu sebenarnya sudah membatalkan pertunangan itu. Masing-masing berasa bingung dan serba salah dengan perkembangan terbaru. Atas nasihat ibunya, Badrul terpaksa meneruskan hubungan dengan Mona. Tertekan dengan apa yang berlaku, Badrul cuba mendapatkan khidmat nasihat psikiatri daripada Dr. Norma. Perbuatan itu menimbulkan rasa sangsi Irfan.

programme.title: Puteri Gunung Ledang S1 Ep09
programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Rayyan seorang lelaki yang kacak tetapi bersikap kaki perempuan. Mereka berkenalan secara lebih dekat tetapi Natasya meletakkan tujuh syarat untuk membuktikan cintanya

programme.desc: Hale menarik perhatian dengan penampilannya yang berbeza dan tingkah laku yang pelik. Dia tinggal di rumah bersejarah dan menakutkan di Nevsehir bersama ibunya, seorang nenek yang tertekan dan ibu saudaranya Azra. Bapa Hale telah hilang sebelum dia dilahirkan dan tidak pernah dilihat lagi. Hale melihat mimpi ngeri malam yang dahsyat; bapanya, yang tidak pernah dilihatnya, menjemputnya ke sebuah rumah tua dan luar biasa.

programme.title: Siccin 6
programme.desc: Seorang gadis dihantui oleh roh jahat di rumah keluarganya. Beberapa perkara buruk mula berlaku di sekeliling rumahnya dan ahli keluarganya. Watak lama bangkit semula dan cuba menyelamatkan keluarga daripada nasib buruk mereka.

programme.title: The Presence
programme.desc: Aom dihantui mimpi ngeri yang tidak dapat dijelaskan. Semasa melawat neneknya, dia mendapat tahu bahawa neneknya yang kelihatan lebih mati daripada hidup sedang melayan dan memberi makan kepada hantu. Adakah Aom akan menerima nasibnya?

programme.title: KL Special Forces
programme.desc: Dua kumpulan pontianak, kedua-duanya keturunan Raja Bersiong, tidak lagi memakan darah manusia. Mereka sebaliknya menggantikannya dengan darah sintetik.

programme.title: Project Wolf Hunting
programme.desc: Membawakan penjenayah berbahaya di atas kapal kargo yang diangkut dari Filipina ke Korea Selatan, dimana mereka melepaskan kuasa jahat ketika percubaan melarikan diri membawa kepada rusuhan.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: Filler
programme.desc: Filler

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal memikirkan cara terbaik untuk menyimpan rahsia tentang batu permata daripada Hariman tanpa menyedari Hariman telah mengetahui batu-batu permata yang dicari selama ini berada dalam simpanan mereka. Imran juga mula mengesyaki bahawa berkemungkinan Hariman adalah salah seorang perompak yang sedang mencari batu-batu permata tersebut. Sementara itu Maira berjaya memujuk ibunya yang kebetulan pulang ke kampung untuk menempah seutas loket bertatahkan sebutir batu milikinya. Dengan perasaan begitu teruja Ibu Maira bergegas pulang semula ke kampung untuk bertemu Maira setelah pemilik sebuah kedai emas bahawa batu milik Maira yang disangka tidak berharga adalah permata asli bernilai belasan ribu ringgit.

programme.title: Double Barrel
programme.desc: Mengenai pasangan muda yang miskin bekerja sebagai pembunuh upahan sehingga mereka diberi tugasan terbaru untuk menghapuskan abang isteri sendiri yang memaksa mereka lari dan bersembunyi daripada kumpulan itu untuk menyelamatkan diri dan bayi mereka.

programme.title: Galaxy Games
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang dewasa muda dihantar ke planet yang jauh untuk bersaing dalam permainan Sol Invictus yang berprestij.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.7 Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang lelaki yang datang dari Kelantan ke Kuala Lumpur untuk bekerja. Ayie datang ke Kuala Lumpur namun di bekalkan oleh ayahnya Yusof dengan patung wayang kulit yang akan menjaganya.

programme.title: Janin Tak Berdosa
programme.desc: Pasangan suami isteri muda Firman dan Julia merancang berbulan madu di Amsterdam selepas Firman mendapat kenaikan pangkat di syarikatnya. Oleh kerana pada masa itu Julia mengandung dan beliau ingin meneruskan percutiannya maka mereka merancang menggugurkan kandungan itu.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.8 Ep8
programme.desc: Azman, craig dan Radhi memilih sebuah flat lama untuk menjkalankan kegiatan dadah mereka. Dari hari pertama Radhi telah di ganggu. Flat yang tak lagi ada penghuni di hantui dengan pelbagai hantu dan syaitan.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Apabila pasukan bola sepak remaja yang terdiri daripada 12 lelaki, berumur 11-16, dan jurulatih mereka berusia 25 tahun terperangkap jauh di dalam gua di Utara Thailand, beribu-ribu sukarelawan dan tentera dari seluruh dunia bersatu dalam perlumbaan melawan masa untuk mencari mereka . Sebaik sahaja kanak-kanak lelaki itu ditemui hidup sepuluh hari kemudian, satu-satunya jalan keluar ialah berenang selama lima jam yang mustahil yang hanya penyelam gua yang pakar boleh bertahan. Di Ireland, juruelektrik kilang kapal terbang dan penyelam gua rekreasi Jim Warny menerima panggilan: "Berapa lama lagi anda boleh berada di sini?" Tiba di Thailand, Jim melangkah keluar dari pesawat dan masuk ke dalam gua - misi tiga hari bermata pisau sedang dijalankan. Berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, THE CAVE menceritakan kisah mendebarkan tentang misi menyelamat antarabangsa terbesar pada zaman moden, dari perspektif unik lelaki dan wanita yang menghadapi keputusan hidup dan mati dan mempamerkan keazaman dan pengorbanan yang tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, yang memuncak dengan keputusan yang berjaya menentang semua kemungkinan.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Adam, Shah dan Danial tiga pemuda di sebuah kampung yang baru balik belajar dalam bidang kejuruteraan dari Jepun. Akibat masalah sukar mendapat pekerjaan Adam telah membeli alat pengesan lembaga bersama-sama dengan alat pengesan, alat penyedut serta alatan yang berkaitan tujuan untuk mengesan dan menangkap lembaga yang merupakan lembaga-lembaga yang sesekali masih wujud dan mengganggu manusia atau keluarga. Ibu-ibu mereka juga tidak senang hati yang mereka tidak ada kerja dan mencebur diri dengan kerja tersebut. Dalam pada itu hasil kerja mereka menjadi tersohor dan tersebar dalam akhbar tempatan. Sementara itu Encik Bad, seorang pengusaha muzium lembaga-lembaga dan anak gadisnya telah berpindah ke rumah baru mereka. Cuma setiap malam kedua-dua mereka mengalami gangguan dipercayai daripada lembaga yang belum dikenal pasti.

programme.title: Hantu Tenggek
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu yang diketuai oleh Tariq yang berpura-pura mengusir tempat berhantu telah diperas ugut oleh Tuan Sidek, seorang pemaju bangunan. Mereka perlu meyakinkan pesaing Tuan Sidek bahawa bangunan tertentu berhantu apabila mereka terperangkap di dalamnya. Kecuali mereka tidak perlu meyakinkan kerana bangunan itu benar-benar dihantui oleh roh yang tidak tenteram. Roh memerlukan bantuan mereka untuk memenuhi hasrat terakhirnya

programme.title: Door Lock
programme.desc: Sebuah thriller yang bermula dengan insiden pembunuhan dengan jejak orang yang tidak dikenali memasuki rumah Kyung Min yang tinggal bersendirian dalam satu bilik.

programme.title: Alam Puaka Ep.1 & 2 Ep1
programme.desc: Kisah-kisah yang dipaparkan di dalam siri ini adalah berdasarkan daripada penceritaan masyarakat umum. Ianya dilakonkan secara fiksyen dan sebarang penambahan tidak berkaitan dengan sesiapa samada hidup atau telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Dina pergi berjumpa bomoh Siam untuk dipulihkan dari dikawal oleh jin Sarakit tetapi bomoh itu tidak dapat membantu. Kesihatan Mariam pula semakin teruk kerana sering diganggu lembaga perempuan sehingga abangnya, Sidek, membawa Ustaz Hambali untuk mengubat Mariam. Sidek telah meminta Rafiq pulang melihat ibunya yang sakit tetapi Rafiq tidak pulang kerana memikirkan keadaan Sarakit yang sarat mengandung. Jali pula sering diganggu hantu tenggek dan perkara ini diceritakan kepada Gato, tetapi Gato tidak mempercayai Jali. Pada satu hari, Jali dijumpai mati dalam keadaan aneh tercacak di batang kayu yang tajam. Kini, giliran Gato pula diganggu dan pada satu pagi, Gato dijumpai Pak Bado tertidur di belukar

programme.title: Daddyku Gangster
programme.desc: Ray ialah ketua geng mencuri kereta mewah, dan terlibat dalam kelab petarungan bawah tanah. Dia tidak mempunyai hubungan yang baik dengan keluarganya, tetapi apabila abangnya Remy dan isteri Remy meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan yang tragis, Ray terkejut kerana abangnya telah menyatakan niatnya dalam wasiat dan telah memilih Ray untuk menjadi penjaganya. dua orang anak - Arisha dan Aidil.

programme.title: Mumun
programme.desc: Mumun dan Juned adalah pasangan yang saling menyayangi. Walau bagaimanapun, Mumun meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan dan Juned sangat kecewa dengannya.

programme.title: Hutang 2D
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan seorang pelukis webtoon yang kuat berangan dan pengecut bernama Ayie yang mempunyai dua masalah dalam hidupnya iaitu hutang bapanya dan cinta terpendamnya pada Shima. Kehadiran dua gangster iaitu Han dan Kit menambahkan satu lagi masalah dalam hidupnya. Segalanya berubah melalui tablet ajaib di mana segala lukisannya menjadi hidup.

programme.title: Mat Som
programme.desc: Mat Som ialah seorang penulis bebas yang bekerja di Kuala Lumpur dan tidak banyak mendapat tugasan dan kecewa kerana tidak mendapat buah fikiran untuk meningkatkan tahap kehidupannya. Selain itu dia gagal menarik perhatian gadis sebelah rumah yang diminatinya, Yam. Dia semakin tertekan apabila bapanya memperkenalkannya kepada Wan Faridah.

programme.title: Minah Manja
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang kehidupan masyarakat di dalam sebuah kampung.Mamak Kutty mahu memperisterikan Minah, anak perempuan kepada seorang guru silat, Ujang Singkap. Ternyata Mamak Kutty mempunyai seorang lagi isteri di India. Akan timbul satu pertelingkahan diantara kedua-dua isteri Mamak Kutty apabila mereka bertemu.

programme.title: Keluarga Comat
programme.desc: Comat tinggal dengan bapanya yang membuka perniagaan membaiki kereta. Pada suatu hari, Borhan menghantar keretanya ke bengkel Pak Comat untuk dibaiki. Di sana Borhan bertemu Comat dan mencadangkan kepada Pak Comat supaya membawa anaknya ke Kuala Lumpur kerana Borhan berminat menjadikan Comat seorang penghibur. Di Kuala Lumpur, pelbagai perkara lucu terjadi.

programme.title: Kepala Angin
programme.desc: Konflik dua pasangan suami isteri yang bertukar peranan. Fandi merupakan seorang jurugambar yang telah jatuh cinta dengan Lydia dan mengahwininya. Lydia bekerja sebagai seorang pengawal keselamatan menyuruh Fandi untuk berhenti kerja selepas keduanya berkahwin. Ini untuk menyenangkan kerja di rumah - tetapi ternyata tidak menjadi.

programme.title: Diva Popular
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pertembungan di antara pelakon senior, Erna Teteyye dengan pelakon baharu, Tasha. Erna ialah seorang pelakon popular yang telah lama berkecimpung dalam perniagaan pertunjukan di Malaysia, dan telah memenangi pelbagai anugerah untuk persembahannya. Pada suatu hari, teman lelakinya, Faizal diberi peluang untuk mengarahkan filem baharu terbitan Julie, namun keadaan menjadi kelam kabut apabila Julie memilih Tasha sebagai heroin filem itu. Pada malam Anugerah Artis Paling Popular Berita Harian, mereka berdua terpilih sebagai finalis untuk anugerah tersebut. Persoalannya, siapakah pemenang dalam pertarungan ini?

programme.title: Gila-Gila Si Pikoy
programme.desc: Pikoy seorang lelaki berasal Filipina yang mempunyai perwatakan sukar untuk difahami, mengembara dari tanah airnya ke Malaysia untuk menerokai sekeliling. Perwatakkannya yang aneh itu membuatkan banyak kejadian lucu berlaku sekitarnya.

programme.title: Bas Konduktor
programme.desc: Tiada tempat untuk dituju, Hairani menaiki sebuah bas ekspres yang dipandu oleh Pie dan Maidin. Mengetahui bahawa Hairani tiada tempat untuk bermalam, dibawanya ke rumah sewa seorang konduktor perempuan yang bekerja di syarikat yang sama. Setelah itu, Hairani diterima bekerja sebagai salah satu konduktor bersama mereka yang lain. Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata.

programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: The New Legend of Shaolin
programme.desc: A Shaolin disciple Hong Xi Guan is tasked to escort the five young shaolin legends who have treasure maps tattooed on their backs to the base of the Anti-Qing Society. They are targeted and hunted by an assassin sent by the Qing government. Can Hong finally keep them safe and complete his mission?

programme.title: Whatever You Want
programme.desc: An illegitimate daughter of a businessman gets three wishes from a genie, Bo. However, Bo's magical power is far from perfect, leading to much hilarity in this charming fantasy comedy.

programme.title: Don't Forget I Love You
programme.desc: Lu Yao suffers from amnesia and forgets about everything that happens yesterday when he wakes up the next day. When Lu Yao meets psychotherapist Xing Yue, they fall in love despite knowing they have no future together, and are determined to love each other no matter what happens...

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tians daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Justice, My Foot!
programme.desc: Chow stars as Sung, a lawyer who uses any means necessary to help his wealthy clients escape the law. Sung retires to the countryside when urged by his wife, but when Mrs Sung encounters a woman whose husband's death has been covered up by corrupted officials, Sung returns to the court for justice to be served.

programme.title: Iron Kung Fu Fist
programme.desc: Liang Kun is a skilled martial arts master who left the martial arts world to protect his lover. However, his disappearance leads to her tragic death and as Liang Kun finds a way to survive in the martial arts world, he fights back to avenge his lovers death with the help of a beggar gang leader.

programme.title: Love Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Love and Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: Zhongkui Kill Demon Legend
programme.desc: The Heavenly Master trapped the spirit of the Demon King so as to save the world from evil. Before he dies, the trapped spirit is transferred into Zhong Kui. As a half human and half demon, Zhong Kui is torn between good and evil. Which side will he finally choose?

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2012
programme.desc: This beloved slapstick comedy series continues as it follows four couples who meet through a dating website. Four men go on a heroic mission to help four women and wind up experiencing a series of mishaps.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tungs mad fate?

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: The Delightful Forest
programme.desc: The legendary hero Wu Sung is sent to a prison in Meng province after murdering his adulterous sister-in-law and her lover. While in prison, the officer Shih En spares Wu the humiliating baton punishment. Owing Shih a favour, Wu decides to help Shih get his restaurant back at all costs when it was forcefully taken over by a local thug.

programme.title: Two Con Men
programme.desc: Two Con Men is a wonderfully twisted, pseudo-romantic comedy in the vein of "Robin Hood" meets "The Sting". Starring Liang Tien as Clever Chan and Chang Ying (who's done over 400 films) as Tricky Ching, it's the age-old competition between a rookie con artist versus the ultimate, experienced flimflam man. It's a game Chen cannot afford to lose, because people's lives - including his own, hang in the balance of good versus evil.

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Qi Ming Xing, an assassin of the Iron Boat Clan, decides to quit the clan. When hunted by the clan, he is saved by Swordsman Zhuo Yi Fan. Zhuo accidentally discovers that Qi is the killer of his wife, but he forgives Qi after knowing Qis guilt over her death. The two finally team up to destroy the evil clan.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Double Bliss tells the story of two students who fall in love and want to wed, but there is one small snag: their parents don't agree! The two ingenious lovebirds come up with what they think is a foolproof plan...They play dead!

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: Threatened by the Yuan who are closing in to rule the whole of China, a band of Song survivors band together to save their prime minister. This bold and fearless heroes fighting for their cause are led by international star, Lo Lieh (Glass Tears, Killer Clans) and Shi Szu (Lovers Destiny), who must fight their way out of trap after trap. But they can't escape them all, and eventually the two end up in prison... it is either death or a fight to the end!

programme.title: Call Of The Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre 2
programme.desc: Only by bringing together the powerful Heaven Sword and the mighty Dragon Sabre can six martial arts sects struggling for supremacy be saved in this thrilling sequel to Chu Yuan's original hit.

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Little Hero
programme.desc: An orphan, Little Bastard is taken on and trained as a fighter by a hermit. When Little Bastard grows up, he feels he is old enough to go out and look for his parents. Luckily for him, he befriends a beggar, Hsiao Yi, who being street-wise, manages to help him find his family, but somehow gets into trouble with the gang.

programme.title: Secret Service Of The Imperial Court
programme.desc: Zhao Bu Fan is the sergeant of the governments secret police. Wang is a cruel and ruthless eunuch who takes over the Emperors ruling power and leads the team of secret agents. After witnessing the atrocities committed by Eunuch Wang, Sergeant Zhao decides to defect but ends up being hunted by his friends, comrades and even his father.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hung escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hung for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hung escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The Trail Of The Broken Blade
programme.desc: Chivalrous swordsman Fung goes in search of another swordsman on the run, Li Yue, in order to reunite him with his love. Though both men meet and end up being close friends, Li Yue did not reveal his true identity until Fungs life is endangered by a gang looking for revenge...

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rongs hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: This film was actually a lively forerunner to the gambling film craze, which eventually swept Asian cinema. Here, it's cardsharp versus cardsharp with a lot more kung-fu action, in a battle of wits and fists to become the king of the casino. The double stings and triple crosses raise in complexity and imagination until what started as an unusual box office risk became a top ten hit of 1976.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: Bat Without Wings
programme.desc: The Bat Without Wings, a notorious rapist-murderer, has returned after a five-year absence. A young swordsman and a convoy master investigate the case and suspect that the Bat may be framed. A saying goes that a treasure map is hidden under the Bats knife, so they try to use that to hunt the real culprit

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: The Magnificent Trio
programme.desc: A group of farmers who are being oppressed by the local magistrates kidnap one of the magistrates daughter in the hope of being heard by the authorities. A wandering swordsman offers his help and aiding him are two fighters who have both switched sides from being the oppressors to the oppressed. The trio fight back against the magistrates!

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Shaolin Intruders
programme.desc: On a routine courier mission, the prestigious Chief was murdered by four mysterious monks. When all evidence pointed to Ching Hua, his friend Lei decides to clear his name by barging in the Shaolin Temple thrice. When Lei thought justice was served for the culprits, he soon realizes the table had turned and the monks stroke again. What follows is a series of intense pursuit for the ultimate villain!

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.desc: Trust no one. Deceive everyone. When idealistic CIA agent Roger Ferris (Di Caprio -- The Departed, Blood Diamond) is stationed in Jordan after being wounded in Iraq, he dedicates his life to stopping further attacks by Al Qaeda. Following a plan that the British employed successfully against the Nazis, Ferris plants the suspicion among the terrorists that their leaders are collaborating with the Americans. But as the stakes rise and Ferris finds himself in the crosshairs, the plot he starts spirals into an outcome he could never have foreseen.

programme.title: Going In Style (2017)
programme.desc: Oscar winners Morgan Freeman, Michael Caine and Alan Arkin team up as lifelong buddies Willie, Joe and Al, who decide to buck retirement and step off the straight-and-narrow for the first time in their lives when their pension fund becomes a corporate casualty, in director Zach Braff's comedy Going In Style. Desperate to pay the bills and come through for their loved ones, the three risk it all by embarking on a daring bid to knock off the very bank that absconded with their money.

programme.title: Batman Begins
programme.desc: As a young boy, Bruce Wayne watched in horror as his millionaire parents were slain in front of him a trauma that leads him to become obsessed with revenge. But the opportunity to avenge his parents' deaths is cruelly taken away from him by fate. Fleeing to the East, where he seeks counsel with the dangerous but honorable ninja cult leader known as Ra's Al-Ghul, Bruce returns to his now decaying Gotham City, which is overrun by organized crime and other dangerous individuals manipulating the system. Meanwhile, Bruce is slowly being swindled out of Wayne Industries, the company he inherited. The discovery of a cave under his mansion, along with a prototype armored suit, leads him to assume a new persona, one which will strike fear into the hearts of men who do wrong; he becomes Batman!!!

programme.title: Red Riding Hood
programme.desc: Valerie is a beautiful young woman torn between two men. She is in love with a brooding outsider Peter, but her parents have arranged for her to marry the wealthy Henry. Unwilling to lose each other, Valerie and Peter are planning to run away together when they learn that Valerie's older sister has been killed by the werewolf that prowls the dark forest surrounding their village. Father Solomon, a famous werewolf hunter, warns that the wolf, who takes human form by day, could be any one of them. As the death toll rises with each moon, Valerie begins to suspect that the werewolf could be someone she loves. Panic grips the town as Valerie discovers that she has a unique connection to the beast.

programme.title: Music And Lyrics
programme.desc: Hugh Grant and Drew Barrymore star as washed-up '80s pop star with a chance for a comeback and his quirky plant lady with a knack for lyrics. Alex Fletcher (Grant--Two Weeks Notice) has been reduced to working the nostalgia circuit at county fairs and amusement parks. The charismatic and talented musician gets a chance at a comeback when reigning pop diva Cora Corman (Haley Bennett) invites him to write and record a duet with her, but there's a problem--Alex hasn't written a song in years; he's never written lyrics . . . and he has to come up with a hit in a matter of days. Enter Sophie Fisher (Barrymore--Lucky You), Alex's beguilingly plant lady, whose flair for words strikes a chord with the struggling songwriter. On the rebound from a bad relationship with the newly famous novelist Sloan Cates (Campbell Scott--Duma), Sophie is reluctant to collaborate with anyone, especially commitment-phobe Alex. Now, Alex and Sophie will have to face their fears--and the music--to find the love and success they both deserve. Written and directed by Marc Lawrence, the writer of the Miss Congeniality films and the writer/director of Two Weeks Notice.

programme.title: The Hangover Part II

In the follow-up to the record-breaking hit comedy, Phil (Bradley Cooper), Stu (Ed Helms), Alan (Zach Galifianakis) and Doug (Justin Bartha) travel to exotic Thailand for Stu's wedding. After Doug's now-unforgettable Las Vegas bachelor party, Stu is not taking any chances and has opted for a safe and subdued pre-wedding brunch. Things don't always go as planned however. What happens in Vegas may stay in Vegas, but what happens in Bangkok can't even be imagined think monkeys, tattoos and the return of Mr. Chow! Acclaimed comedy filmmaker Todd Phillips reunites with his comic quartet of over-indulged stars for another globe-trotting howl at the moon with the "Wolfpack."
